  "3219820": {
    "name": "Road Motel Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3219820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/2dfa74ceeeb5ab9fb62f35ed44a673c7.poster.avif?t=1744937220\" width=600 height=54 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/2dfa74ceeeb5ab9fb62f35ed44a673c7.webm?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/2dfa74ceeeb5ab9fb62f35ed44a673c7.mp4?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Road Motel Simulator</strong> 是一款合作模拟游戏，让您管理自己的汽车旅馆，旅馆位于传奇的 66 号公路中段的沙漠中。接待疲惫的旅客，为他们提供最高水平的舒适体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与朋友一起游玩</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/f777c19605182ff54ff68a5c8ea22b59.poster.avif?t=1744937220\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/f777c19605182ff54ff68a5c8ea22b59.webm?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/f777c19605182ff54ff68a5c8ea22b59.mp4?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>与最多 4 位朋友一起在多人模式中经营您的汽车旅馆。合作高效地发展您的业务，在空闲时间享受旅馆提供的设施，与团队放松心情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>接待旅客</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/a82c386ba5e50d5edb964b8eece6c648.poster.avif?t=1744937220\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/a82c386ba5e50d5edb964b8eece6c648.webm?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/a82c386ba5e50d5edb964b8eece6c648.mp4?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在汽车旅馆的接待处欢迎您的客人。他们对您设施的兴趣将取决于之前访客留下的评论以及您已接待的客人数目。从房间价格、食物供应，到房间清洁程度和保持安静的规定，所有这些都会影响客人的满意度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>扩展您的旅馆</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/9ca4fe494bcfc5b2ba32a5725096fb59.poster.avif?t=1744937220\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/9ca4fe494bcfc5b2ba32a5725096fb59.webm?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/9ca4fe494bcfc5b2ba32a5725096fb59.mp4?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>将赚取的资金用于扩展您的旅馆，并进一步发展业务。除了增加更多房间，您还可以为客人提供各种设施，例如餐厅、游泳池甚至赌场。这将帮助提升整体客人满意度，从而带来更好的评论。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>装修与翻新</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/7821053062041aa71a1ab420a8dd16c9.poster.avif?t=1744937220\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/7821053062041aa71a1ab420a8dd16c9.webm?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/7821053062041aa71a1ab420a8dd16c9.mp4?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>您可以完全控制汽车旅馆房间的装饰风格。只需满足基本需求，例如提供床和淋浴设施。随着游戏进展，您将解锁新的家具和装饰风格。您还可以使用特殊的翻新工具更改墙壁和天花板的颜色，快速调整旅馆的设计以匹配您的愿景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经营旅馆商店</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/56f8cbeec28d5c1295a6dfd2d3afae83.poster.avif?t=1744937220\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/56f8cbeec28d5c1295a6dfd2d3afae83.webm?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/56f8cbeec28d5c1295a6dfd2d3afae83.mp4?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>接待区域有足够的空间放置货架。利用这些空间展示各种物品，例如食品或旅游指南，以增加收入并吸引更多旅客对旅馆产生兴趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>雇用员工</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/7bcb88d9cae84495b6156718bc9e6d41.poster.avif?t=1744937220\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/7bcb88d9cae84495b6156718bc9e6d41.webm?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/7bcb88d9cae84495b6156718bc9e6d41.mp4?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>您不需要独自处理所有事情。在游戏中，您可以雇用员工协助管理旅馆的日常运营。此外，当他们不当班时，也可以成为您的客人，享受您为客人准备的设施。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>替代收入来源</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/cd45904b8fecda6a36cf322f18204601.poster.avif?t=1744937220\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/cd45904b8fecda6a36cf322f18204601.webm?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219820/extras/cd45904b8fecda6a36cf322f18204601.mp4?t=1744937220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你是否觉得有些客人太贪心，几乎没在你的汽车旅馆留下任何钱？与其向他们要钱，不如自己动手拿。夜晚时，用开锁工具偷偷进入他们的车内，将找到的贵重物品卖到当地的当铺。</p>",
